<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV8">
<l>ātiyāṉa vāṉavarkku maṇṭamāya vappuṟat</l>
<l>tātiyāṉa vāṉavarkku mātiyāṉa vātinī</l>
<l>ātiyāṉa vāṉavāṇa rantakālam nīyuraitti</l>
<l>ātiyāṉa kālaniṉṉai yāvarkāṇa vallarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You are the god who is the original Creator of the celestials who are gods [who create],</l>
<l>[and] of the celestials who are gods on the other side, namely, the sky!</l>
<l>You have pronounced the end-time of the inhabitants of the sky who are primeval.</l>
<l>O Time who are the origin! Who is capable of seeing You?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
